OL,3,CMan jailed for murder of dad who tried
OL,4,Cto prevent attack at neighbour's home
OL,6,FGeorge Ness has been jailed for life
OL,7,Ffor fatally attacking John Smyth in a
OL,8,F"drink and drug-fuelled rage", as
OL,9,FGregg Easteal reports
OL,11,FA man has been jailed for life with a
OL,12,Fminimum term of 22 years for murdering
OL,13,Fa dad-of-two who intervened during a
OL,14,Fviolent disturbance at his neighbour's
OL,15,Fproperty in Newcastle.
