OL,3,CMan jailed for murder of dad who tried
OL,4,Cto prevent attack at neighbour's home
OL,6,FGeorge Ness was "completely out of
OL,7,Fcontrol" when he inflicted skull
OL,8,Ffractures and unsurvivable brain
OL,9,Finjuries on John Smyth, 63, originally
OL,10,Ffrom Glasgow, then stamped on his body
OL,11,Fas he lay bleeding and unconscious.
OL,13,FThe killer rifled through the dying
OL,14,Fman's pockets and stole his phone
OL,15,Fafter the three-minutes of violence at
OL,16,Fthe flat in Wallsend in September last
OL,17,Fyear.
