OL,3,CMan jailed for murder of dad who tried
OL,4,Cto prevent attack at neighbour's home
OL,6,FNess, 41, of Avon Avenue, North
OL,7,FShields, North Tyneside, denied murder
OL,8,Fbut was found guilty by a jury at
OL,9,FNewcastle Crown Court.
OL,11,FOn Monday (10 March), he was sentenced
OL,12,Fto life behind bars and told he must
OL,13,Fserve a minimum 22 years for the
OL,14,Fkilling, Ness laughed loudly while
OL,15,FJudge Paul Sloan KC was talking.
OL,17,FJudge Sloan said Mr Smyth had managed
OL,18,Fto block some of the blows with his
OL,19,Farm but he was hit between five and
OL,20,Feight times to the head.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/7
