OL,3,CMan jailed for murder of dad who tried
OL,4,Cto prevent attack at neighbour's home
OL,6,FThe judge told him: "This was a
OL,7,Fparticularly brutal attack involving
OL,8,Fsustained and extensive violence, blow
OL,9,Fupon blow upon blow upon blow
OL,10,Fdelivered to the deceased,
OL,11,Fparticularly to his head, which you
OL,12,Fspecifically targeted and delivered
OL,13,Feven after he had gone to the ground."
OL,15,FThe court heard Mr Smyth, who had just
OL,16,Fmoved to North Shields, North
OL,17,FTyneside, from Derby, had been at the
OL,18,Fhome of a female neighbour, who Ness
OL,19,Fhad earlier bought crack cocaine from.
