OL,3,CMan jailed for murder of dad who tried
OL,4,Cto prevent attack at neighbour's home
OL,6,FFootage released by Northumbria Police
OL,7,Fshows George Ness on his way to the
OL,8,Faddress where he carried out the
OL,9,Fattack, and then leaving the area
OL,11,FThe deadly violence happened on 22
OL,12,FSeptember 2024 when Ness turned up
OL,13,Fwanting more drugs, which he did not
OL,14,Fhave the money to pay for and had
OL,15,Fwarned her "I'm coming in", while in
OL,16,F"a drink and drug-fuelled rage".
OL,18,FThe court heard Mr Smyth picked up,
OL,19,Fbut did not use, a craft knife and
OL,20,Fscrew driver to confront Ness outside
OL,21,Fbut was met with deadly violence.
