OL,3,CMan jailed for murder of dad who tried
OL,4,Cto prevent attack at neighbour's home
OL,6,FNess had claimed he was acting in self
OL,7,Fdefence.
OL,9,FBut Judge Sloan said: "The deceased
OL,10,Fwas trying to prevent an attack by you
OL,11,Fon his neighbour's property. It is he
OL,12,Fwho was acting in self defence of his
OL,13,Fneighbour and her property."
OL,15,FThe court heard Mr Smyth's death has
OL,16,Fleft his family devastated and
OL,17,Ftraumatised.
