OL,3,CMan jailed for murder of dad who tried
OL,4,Cto prevent attack at neighbour's home
OL,6,FHis daughter, a student, said in an
OL,7,Fimpact statement she struggles to
OL,8,Fbelieve he has gone or understand why
OL,9,Fand added: "Things will never be the
OL,10,Fsame now my dad has gone."
OL,12,FHis son said the loss is "overwhelming
OL,13,Fand all-consuming" and added: "I feel
OL,14,Fsick to my stomach his life ended in
OL,15,Fthis way."
OL,17,FJudge Sloan added: "No sentence I am
OL,18,Fpermitted by law to impose could even
OL,19,Fbegin to ease their suffering and
OL,20,Fpain, suffering and pain which will
OL,21,Fremain with them always."
